# --- Market + news providers (recommendations explain drawer + market router) ---
# Exact variable names must match app/core/config.py.
#
# Docker Compose:
# - Keys in ONLY investments-microservice/.env are loaded into the `investment` container via
#   docker-compose `env_file` (repo root `.env` is merged too if present).
# - Do NOT rely on `${VAR:-}` in compose for secrets if the host env is empty — that used to
#   override env_file with blank values (fixed in docker-compose.yml).
#
# Local `uvicorn` / pytest:
# - Use a real file named `.env` here (copy from this example). `.env.example` is not loaded.
#
# TwelveData / Alpha Vantage: primarily market data (quotes/bars). Headlines use Benzinga + Finnhub
# (see app/services/news_router.py); Alpha Vantage in NEWS_PROVIDER_ORDER is reserved for future use.
